short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Control your chrome browser from your Omnibox. Start apps, open downloads, options and much more!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This small extentions allows you to start common browser features in a quick matter using the Omnibox. 
Just ype "start" with the command and you are ready to go!

Features:
* Quickly start most common features like downloads, extensions, settings and many more. 
* Lightweight.
* Support for 18 commands and counting!
* List of all the available commands.

What is to come?
* Even more commands!
* Make your own commands.

This extension does not track any information. Not what you type in, not where you are going and not a single thing about your computer.
